{"tid":260190,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益）呢舊拱起既野係咪j黎？","createTime":"2017-05-27T13:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T01:53:00.000Z","uid":995,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d45b28bc358e74fe85a870f9b864f149757e640d","tid":260190,"uid":995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"話說我呀妹今日搭小巴<br />\n搭搭下覺得佢隔離個男人有d奇怪<br />\n望下發覺佢下面拱起咗<br />\n起初頭一眼以為佢伸咗隻手入去r <br />\n但隔咗陣 望真d 發現原來唔係手 唔知係咩<br />\n係呢個時候佢發現呢個男人有不時望下佢<br />\n所以就影低咗 想問過明白<br />\n<br />\n佢sd 咗俾我睇 但我唔sure <br />\n因為佢條褲咁窄 冇可能頂到咁 <br />\n除非佢真係變態 攞咗出黎<br />\n但佢問d女仔fd 佢地就話係j<br />\n<br />\n所以想上黎求個明白<br />\n利申：唔係未搞情楚就公審 係想問下大家覺得係咩<br />\n如果係j  希望各位女性小心<br />\n如果唔係 希望遲下有相同case 大家唔好又誤會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/214557_cfb7c628b8a89f1f34ce72c20c737f14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F214557_cfb7c628b8a89f1f34ce72c20c737f14.jpg&h=0002b2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/214559_347c7eb2ba92ed5de9fed601c548495f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F214559_347c7eb2ba92ed5de9fed601c548495f.jpg&h=0bdc2a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/214600_c3c5ea55564a9bd8bb91ab0250c996df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F214600_c3c5ea55564a9bd8bb91ab0250c996df.jpg&h=7e59df9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/214608_a8c7ad992a15c979726a8fdde08093c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F214608_a8c7ad992a15c979726a8fdde08093c2.jpg&h=f0c12bc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97bfce29c7e3fe54335d0d8ff19220109b7fa753","tid":260190,"uid":10313,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201